Package: nutrientprofiler
Title: Nutrient Model Profiler
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Alex", "Coleman", , "a.coleman1@leeds.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7723-3222"))
Description: This package implements functions to help assess 
    product information against the UK Nutrient Profiling Model (2004/5).
    These scores can be used as part of scoping HFSS when determining product placement.
